e%22%3A%22ED%20Summons%20Jharkhand%20CM%20Soren%20Again%20in%20a%20New%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F12112643%2FFgpYtIoUAAAFk_-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EJharkhand%20chief%20minister%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20official%20sources%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fed-summons-jharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-in-money-laundering-case%2Farticle67172397.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20agency%20on%20August%2014%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20Soren%20was%20also%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20last%20November%2C%20however%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20another%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20illegal%20mining%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20word%20yet%20on%20the%20reason%20for%20questioning%20Soren%20this%20time%20around%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fjharkhand%2Fed-summons-jharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-in-money-laundering-case-2639561%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20sources%2C%20that%20he%20will%20be%20questioned%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20an%20alleged%20defence%20land%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20Jharkhand%20unit%20chief%2C%20Deepak%20Prakash%2C%20demanded%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20actively%20connived%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccorrupt%20bureaucrats%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state%20resulting%20in%20the%20alleged%20scam%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20requested%20the%20ED%20to%20investigate%20the%20case.%20Today%2C%20the%20result%20is%20that%20after%20the%20illegal%20mining%20case%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20money%20laundering%20with%20respect%20to%20land%20held%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20Prakash%20as%20saying.%20Prakash%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20the%20first%20to%20expose%20the%20alleged%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20already%20been%20investigating%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20land%20deals%2C%20including%20one%20related%20to%20defence%20land%2C%20wherein%20a%20group%20of%20land%20mafia%2C%20middlemen%2C%20and%20bureaucrats%20allegedly%20connived%20to%20forge%20deeds%20and%20documents%20dating%20as%20long%20back%20as%201932.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20PMLA%20court%20had%20already%20arrested%20Jharkhand%20IAS%20officer%20Chhavi%20Ranjan%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20He%20was%20questioned%20for%20nearly%2010%20hours%20on%20April%2024.%20The%20probe%20agency%20carried%20out%20searches%20on%20April%2013%20at%20premises%20linked%20to%20Ranjan%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Bihar.%20Several%20people%20were%20arrested%20after%20the%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20ED%20summoned%20him%2C%20Soren%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%207%2C%20had%20accused%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20misusing%20federal%20agencies%20to%20disturb%20his%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fmoney-laundering-case-enforcement-directorate-summons-jharkhand-chief-minister-hemant-soren-for-questioning-on-august-14%2Fcid%2F1957722%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp