5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESushmita%20Sen%20reveals%20that%20Gauri%20Sawant%20on%20whom%20her%20web%20show%20Taali%20is%20based%20hasn't%20seen%20the%20show%20but%20said%20that%20whatever%20Sushmita%20has%20done%20in%20the%20show%20is%20right.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Appointments%2C%20Assets%2C%20Leaves%3A%20House%20Panel's%20Big%20Remarks%20On%20Senior%20Judges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20of%20backward%20communities%2C%20women%20and%20minorities%20in%20higher%20judiciary%20is%20below%20the%20desired%20level%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20country's%20social%20diversity%2C%20a%20Parliamentary%20panel%20has%20said%20in%20its%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20also%20recommended%20bringing%20a%20law%20making%20it%20mandatory%20for%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20court%20judges%20to%20disclose%20their%20assets%20annually%20to%20an%20appropriate%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Personnel%2C%20Public%20Grievances%2C%20Law%20and%20Justice%2C%20chaired%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20presented%20its%20133rd%20report%20on%20%26quot%3BJudicial%20Processes%20and%20their%20reform%26quot%3B%20to%20both%20the%20Houses%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20the%20lack%20of%20caste-based%20reservation%20in%20appointments%20to%20high%20courts%20and%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20said%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20suffers%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiversity%20deficit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20reservation%20in%20the%20judicial%20appointments%20at%20High%20Courts%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20level%2C%20the%20Committee%20feels%20that%20adequate%20representation%20of%20various%20sections%20of%20Indian%20society%20will%20further%20strengthen%20the%20trust%2C%20credibility%2C%20and%20acceptability%20of%20the%20Judiciary%20among%20the%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20out%20of%20the%20601%20high%20court%20appointments%20since%202018%2C%20457%20were%20from%20the%20general%20category%2C%2018%20from%20Scheduled%20Classes%2C%209%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%2072%20from%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2032%20from%20minority%20communities%20and%2091%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20recommended%20that%20the%20collegiums%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20courts%20should%20back%20an%20adequate%20number%20of%20women%20and%20candidates%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20while%20making%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20flagged%20vacations%20of%20judges%20and%20recommended%20that%20judges%20follow%20a%20rotational%20model%20instead%20of%20courts%20shutting%20for%20vacations.%20It%20said%20pendency%20of%20cases%20was%20piling%20up%20due%20to%20the%20long%20vacations%20of%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20there%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20institutionalise%20the%20mechanism%20of%20regular%20filing%20of%20assets%20by%20the%20judges%20and%20putting%20it%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20%26quot%3B...the%20Committee%20recommends%20the%20government%20to%20bring%20about%20appropriate%20legislation%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%20for%20judges%20of%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20(Supreme%20Court%20and%20High%20Courts)%20to%20furnish%20their%20property%20returns%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%20to%20the%20appropriate%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20belies%20logic%20that%20judges%20don't%20need%20to%20disclose%20their%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20that%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20holding%20that%20the%20public%20has%20a%20right%20to%20know%20the%20assets%20of%20those%20standing%20for%20elections%20as%20MPs%20or%20MLAs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20parliamentary%20panel%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691559480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliamentary-committee-sushil-kumar-modi-supreme-court-appointments-assets-leaves-house-panels-big-remarks-on-senior-judges-4281889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20representation%20of%20backward%20communities%2C%20women%20and%20minorities%20in%20higher%20judiciary%20is%20below%20the%20desired%20level%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20country's%20social%20diversity%2C%20a%20Parliamentary%20panel%20has%20said%20in%20its%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliamentary-committee-sushil-kumar-modi-supreme-court-appointments-assets-leaves-house-panels-big-remarks-on-senior-judges-4281889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliamentary-committee-sushil-kumar-modi-supreme-court-appointments-assets-leaves-house-panels-big-remarks-on-senior-judges-4281889%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliamentary-committee-sushil-kumar-modi-supreme-court-appointments-assets-leaves-house-panels-big-remarks-on-senior-judges-4281889%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20lottery%20player%20wins%20historic%20%241.58bn%20jackpot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691559480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-jackpot-lotteyr-lottery_6244964.jpg%3F20230809064743%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flucky-player-wins-158bn-jackpot-in-third-largest-ever-in-us-history-12936450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Someone%20in%20Florida%20has%20won%20a%20%241.58%20billion%20Mega%20Millions%20jackpot%20-%20the%20third-largest%20ever%20in%20US%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag