0when%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20speak%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20will%20speak%20today.%20He%20will%20begin%20from%20our%20side%20at%20noon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20would%20start%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20backed%20by%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%20The%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20Kaliabor%20MP%20and%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20the%20reports%20said%20he%20would%20step%20aside%20to%20let%20Mr%20Gandhi%20initiate%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20the%20House%20met%20yesterday%2C%20it%20was%20Mr%20Gogoi%20who%20started%20the%20debate.%20The%20treasury%20benches%20did%20not%20lose%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20swipe%2C%20with%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20to%20hear%20him%20(Mr%20Gandhi)%20speak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20responded%20that%20whatever%20is%20discussed%20in%20the%20Speaker's%20chamber%20stays%20there.%20He%20questioned%20if%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20if%20he%20cited%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20in%20the%20chamber.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20MPs%2C%20led%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20dared%20him%20to%20speak%20out.%20The%20chaos%20continued%20before%20Mr%20Gogoi%20eventually%20started%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Congress%20sources%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20let%20Mr%20Gogoi%20begin%20the%20debate%20primarily%20due%20to%20two%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20Mr%20Gogoi%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Northeast%20region%20and%20his%20beginning%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-trust%20motion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20holds%20a%20symbolic%20significance.%20Also%2C%20replacing%20him%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20is%20back%20as%20an%20MP%20would%20only%20expose%20the%20party%20to%20attacks%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20never%20loses%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20the%20dynasty%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%20of%20not%20fielding%20Mr%20Gandhi%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20debate%20was%20the%20absence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20the%20House.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20likely%20to%20speak%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20tomorrow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20are%20well%20aware%20that%20they%20do%20not%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%20as%20far%20as%20numbers%20are%20concerned.%20The%20move%20is%20primarily%20to%20force%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20address%20the%20House%20on%20Manipur%20and%20target%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%20The%20party%2C%20therefore%2C%20does%20not%20want%20to%20provide%20any%20opportunity%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20turn%20the%20situation%20to%20its%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20confirmation%2C%20there%20was%20confusion%20regarding%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20Lok%20Sabha%20address.%20While%20some%20sources%20in%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20saying%20he%20may%20speak%20today%2C%20reports%20said%20he%20is%20scheduled%20to%20attend%20a%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20is%20back%20as%20an%20MP%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stayed%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20over%20the%20'Modi%20surname'%20remark.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691557560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fu6bhu8go_rahul-gandhi_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-prime-minister-narendra-modi-parliament-live-no-trust-debate-no-confidence-motion-when-will-rahul-gandhi-speak-big-question-as-no-trust-d-4281768%22%2C%22su