WhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.02-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImphal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20recently%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-most-unclaimed-bodies-lying-in-morgues-are-of-infiltrators-government-tells-supreme-court-news-307387%5C%22%3E%20claimed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20of%20the%20bodies%20still%20in%20morgues%20in%20Manipur%20are%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D.%20Mehta%20is%20representing%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20the%20state%20government%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20the%20ethnic%20conflict.%20Senior%20advocate%20Ranjit%20Kumar%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20High%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20of%20Manipur%2C%20submitted%20that%20the%20influx%20of%20undocumented%20immigrants%20from%20Myanmar%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20unrest%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20SG%20nor%20Kumar%20provided%20any%20evidence%20for%20these%20allegations.%20The%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Fitlf-slams-sg-tushar-mehta-over-his-remarks-of-kuki-zo-tribals-as-infiltrators%2F%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20claim%2C%20condemning%20his%20words.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Mr.%20Mehta%20suggesting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D%20were%20roaming%20freely%20in%20Imphal%20until%20May%203%2C%202023%3F%20Were%20they%20plucked%20out%20from%20the%20general%20population%20with%20precision%20by%20rampaging%20mobs%2C%20while%20all%20tribal%20Indian%20citizens%20were%20left%20untouched%3F%20Were%20state%20agencies%20helping%20the%20mobs%20identify%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20ITLF%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20killed%20in%20Imphal%20are%20not%20infiltrators%20but%20legitimate%20Indian%20citizens%20who%20are%20government%20employees%2C%20university%20students%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20mothers%20and%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-tribal-women-group-seeks-withdrawal-of-remarks-by-solicitor-general-in-sc%2Farticleshow%2F102502452.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20the%20UNAU%20Tribal%20Forum%2C%20Delhi%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20loose%20and%20unfounded%20remark%20from%20the%20solicitor%20general%20of%20India%20is%20unbecoming%20(of%20him)%2C%20unacceptable%20and%20abhorrent.%20It%20is%20deeply%20hurtful%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20dead%2C%20who%20till%20today%2C%20are%20unable%20to%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20SG%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20all%20the%20bodies%20of%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis%20from%20Manipur%20who%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20on%20May%203%20have%20been%20claimed.%20However%2C%20during%20our%20reporting%20from%20Manipur%20and%20in%20conversation%20with%20families%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20kin%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20repeatedly%20told%20that%20Kukis%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20claim%20their%20relatives%E2%80%99%20bodies%20from%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20RIIMS%20and%20JNIMS%20Hospital%2C%20as%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20because%20of%20the%20security%20situation.%20Similarly%2C%20Meiteis%20are%20having%20trouble%20travelling%20to%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20tribal%20communities%20petitioning%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fsupreme-court-blasts-manipur-police-for-lethargic-and-tardy-investigations%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20categorically%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20were%20118%20bodies%20of%20tribal%20people%20lying%20in%20the%20morgues%20of%20Imphal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20bodies%20are%20unidentified%20for%20months.%20They%20are%20rotting%3B%20we%20cannot%20go%20there%20to%20identify%20them.%20No%20attempt%20is%20being%20made%20to%20help%20us%20identify.%E2%80%9D%20The%20court%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20SG%20to%20inquire%20with%20the%20government%20on%20the%20provisions%20of%20compensation%20to%20those%20affected%20and%20to%20report%20to%20it%20the%20proposed%20mechanism%20for%20determining%20the%20amount%20and%20its%20disbursement%2C%20as%20well%20identifying%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20SG%E2%80%99s%20shocking%20remarks%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%201%2C%20which%20supported%20the%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20press%20statements%20that%20the%20Kuki%20community%20has%20been%20harbouring%20undocumented%20Myanmar%20immigrants%20and%20infiltrators%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20all%20the%20valley-based%20districts%20of%20the%20northeastern%20state%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20bodies%20lying%20at%20different%20hospitals.%20In%20the%20seven%20districts%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%2C%20152%20deaths%20had%20been%20reported.%20Of%20these%2C%20only%2022%20bodies%20are%20officially%20%E2%80%98unidentified%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20able%20to%20determine%20the%20identity%20of%20three%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20areas%2C%20bodies%20of%20Kuki%20victims%20are%20still%20in%20hospital%20morgues%20despite%20being%20identified.%20This%20is%20as%20families%20are%20unable%20to%20travel.%20In%20Kuki-dominated%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%2C%20similarly%2C%20Meitei%20victims%E2%80%99%20bodies%20remain%20in%20hospital%20morgues%20despite%20being%20iden