3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChurachandpur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Total%20number%20of%20dead%20bodies%3A%2039%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20All%20bodies%20are%20identified%2C%20with%2035%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%204%20to%20Meitei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKangpokpi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Total%20number%20of%20dead%20bodies%3A%2011%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%93%20All%20bodies%20are%20identified%2C%20with%205%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%206%20to%20Meitei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20last%20updated%20data%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20on%20August%205%2C%20the%20total%20deaths%20count%20is%20at%20142.%20However%2C%20data%20received%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20districts%20mentioned%20above%20makes%20it%20a%20total%20of%20152%20deaths.%20The%20government%20has%20identified%20bodies%20of%20130%20of%20these%20people%2C%20and%2022%20remain%20unidentified.%20Of%20those%2022%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20identified%20three%20%E2%80%93%20so%20the%20new%20number%20from%20the%20unidentified%20we%20can%20confirm%20is%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KSO%20too%20has%20been%20gathering%20a%20list%20of%20the%20people%20killed%20in%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%203%2C%20focusing%20on%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20Their%20list%20states%20that%20136%20Kukis%20have%20died%20so%20far%2C%20out%20of%20which%2023%20are%20women.%20The%20list%20was%20last%20updated%20on%20July%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20in%20court%20that%20the%20unidentified%20and%20unclaimed%20bodies%20belong%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar.%20General%20secretary%20of%20the%20KSO%20D.J.%20Haokip%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20KSO%20is%20ready%20to%20verify%20all%20the%20bodies%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20morgue%20with%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards%20and%20all%20the%20relevant%20documents%E2%80%9D%20if%20provided%20with%20security.%20He%20also%20stated%20that%20most%20of%20those%20killed%20were%20government%20employees%2C%20and%20asked%20how%20alleged%20foreigners%20could%20have%20got%20government%20jobs%20in%20India.%20Haokip%20said%20Mehta%20is%20misinformed%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20KSO%20be%20provided%20with%20security%20to%20enter%20Imphal%20to%20verify%20the%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20last%20updated%20its%20data%20in%20July%2C%20and%20the%20current%20numbers%20could%20be%20different%2C%20but%20the%20names%20received%20from%20sources%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20Manipur%20matches%20the%20list%20that%20the%20KSO%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20only%20a%20few%20families%20have%20received%20compensation%20so%20far%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20too%20only%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20share.%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20promised%20that%20each%20family%20would%20get%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20but%20so%20far%20no%20one%20has%20received%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691555197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095301%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.02-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsg-tushar-mehtas-claim-that-unclaimed-bodies-in-manipur-belong-to-infiltrators-is-unfounded%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20has%20been%20able%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20confirm%20only%2019%20bodies%20are%20unidentified%20in%20Manipur.%20However%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20even%20identified%20bodies%20remain%20in%20hospital%20morgues%20as%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20are%20being%20unable%20to%20travel%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2