20I%2C%20after%20losing%20the%20first%20two.%20Surya%2C%20who%20scored%20a%2044-ball%2083%20in%20the%20match%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20where%20questions%20about%20his%20ODI%20form%20also%20emerged.%20The%20explosive%20batter%20that%20his%20numbers%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20have%20been%20far%20from%20impressive%20and%20he%20finds%20no%20shame%20in%20admitting%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurykumar's%20vintage%20performance%20with%20bat%20and%20Tilak%20Varma's%20unbridled%2049*%20kept%20India%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20action%20as%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20clinched%20victory%20in%20the%20third%20ODI%20by%207%20wickets%20at%20the%20Providence%20Stadium%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20very%20honest%2C%20my%20one-day%20numbers%20are%20absolutely%20bad%20and%20there's%20no%20shame%20in%20admitting%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Suryakumar%20said%20after%20his%20match-winning%20knock%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%20''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20talk%20about%20honesty%20and%20you%20have%20to%20be%2C%20but%20how%20you%20can%20improve%20is%20more%20important.%20Rohit%20(Sharma)%20and%20Rahul%20(Dravid)%20sir%20have%20told%20me%20that%20this%20is%20the%20format%20that%20I%20do%20not%20play%20much%20so%20you%20have%20to%20play%20it%20more%20and%20think%20about%20it.%20If%20you%20are%20batting%20in%20the%20last%2010-15%20overs%2C%20think%20about%20what%20you%20can%20do%20for%20the%20team.%20It%20is%20in%20my%20hand%20now%20how%20to%20change%20the%20responsibility%20into%20an%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Suryakumar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar's%20high-risk%2C%20360-degree%20batting%20has%20won%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20acclaim%20and%20success%20in%20T20Is.%20In%2051%20T20Is%20and%2049%20innings%2C%20he%20has%20scored%201%2C780%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2045.64%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20174.33.%20He%20has%20scored%20three%20centuries%20and%2014%20fifties%20in%20the%20format.%20He%20won%20the%20'ICC%20T20I%20Player%20of%20the%20Year'%20award%20in%202022%20for%20his%20performances%20and%20is%20also%20the%20number%201%20batter%20worldwide%20in%20this%20format.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Suryakumar%2C%20'SKY'%20has%20not%20been%20the%20limit%20in%20ODIs.%20In%2026%20ODIs%20and%2024%20innings%2C%20he%20has%20managed%20just%20511%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2024.33%2C%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Suryakumar%20got%20a%20solid%20start%20in%20ODI%20cricket.%20In%20his%20first%20six%20innings%2C%20he%20scored%20261%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2065.25%2C%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%20His%20last%20half-century%20was%20in%20February%202022%20against%20West%20Indies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20been%20downhill%20for%20the%20batter.%20In%2018%20innings%20that%20followed%20since%20his%20last%20fifty%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20just%20250%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2014.70%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%2035.%20This%20also%20includes%20three%20successive%20golden%20ducks%20against%20Australia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batter%20admitted%20that%20he%20feels%20more%20used%20to%20the%20T20I%20style%20of%20batting%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Men%20in%20Blue%20play%20this%20format%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20comparison%20to%20ODIs%20and%20he%20finds%20the%2050-over%20format%20as%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20playing%20T20%20format%20so%20much%20that%20I%20have%20gotten%20used%20to%20it.%20One-day%20is%20a%20format%20that%20I%20do%20not%20play%20much%20and%20I%20find%20it%20as%20the%20most%20challenging%20format.%20You%20have%20to%20bat%20differently%20-%20if%20a%20wicket%20falls%20early%2C%20you%20have%20to%20bat%20a%20little%20like%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20then%20in%20between%20you%20try%20to%20accelerate%20ball%20by%20ball%20and%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20T20%20approach.%20So%20I%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20apply%20what%20the%20team%20management%20has%20told%20me%20so%20far%20about%20the%20format.%20I%20try%20to%20take%20some%20time%20in%20ODIs%20as%20per%20the%20time%20and%20then%20play%20my%20game%20towards%20the%20end.%20I%20will%20try%20to%20repay%20the%20faith%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20his%20knock%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20different%2C%20just%20batting%20like%20he%20has%20been%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20for%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20same%20day%20as%20these%20last%20two%20years.%20I%20went%20out%20and%20expressed%20myself.%20Everything%20kept%20falling%20in%20place%20with%20the%20way%20I%20batted%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suryakumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20missing%20on%20a%20potential%20hundred%2C%20Suryakumar%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20care%20much%20about%20milestones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tilak%20Varma's%20batting%20in%20the%20series%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTilak%20for%20his%20age%2C%20is%20showing%20amazing%20maturity.%20The%20way%20he%20batted%20is%20great.%20We%20have%20batted%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20together.%20He%20has%20done%20the%20same%20there.%20All%20credit%20goes%20to%20him%2C%20he%20is%20a%20star.%20He%20is%20clear%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20knows%20his%20game.%20He%20is%20very%20mentally%20strong%2C%20which%20is%20important%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20win%2C%20India%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20the%20series%20alive%20by%202-1.%20There%20are%20two%20more%20games%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691554920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F13modup_suryakumar-pc_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-in