20Expression%20of%20Humility%2C%20Tenacity%20and%20Determination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08175608%2FGaddaar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20my%20first%20year%20of%20post%20graduation%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20when%20I%20came%20across%20Gaddar%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20That%20was%20more%20than%20four%20decades%20ago.%20The%20Janata%20Party%20had%20come%20to%20power%20and%20several%20flowers%20of%20democratic%20rights%20suddenly%20blossomed%20as%20it%20were%2C%20after%20two%20years%20of%20emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%20several%20student%20groups%20sprouting%20at%20the%20university%2C%20I%20joined%20the%20Radical%20Students%20Center%20(RSC)%2C%20a%20small%20student%20group%20that%20discussed%20struggles%20launched%20by%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20RSC%20believed%20in%20creating%20a%20new%20humane%20order%20for%20the%20peasants%20and%20workers%20in%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20we%20were%20exposed%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20a%20cultural%20group%20called%20the%20Jana%20Natya%20Mandali.%20It%20relentlessly%20propagated%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20against%20oppression%20in%20rural%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20architect%20of%20that%20mandali%20was%20a%20short%2C%20well-built%2C%20plucky%20man%20with%20a%20beard%20and%20a%20stick%20in%20his%20hand%2C%20always%20wearing%20a%20dhoti%20like%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20His%20name%20was%20Gaddar%2C%20a%20radical%20folk%20singer%20and%20balladeer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaddar%20was%20an%20engineering%20student%20in%20Osmania%20University%20who%20gave%20up%20his%20studies%20while%20some%20of%20his%20classmates%20went%20on%20to%20become%20experts%20in%20different%20fields%20of%20engineering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20one%20of%20Gaddar%E2%80%99s%20close%20friends%20and%20classmate%20%E2%80%93%20then%20a%20professor%20of%20aeronautical%20engineering%20in%20Washington%20University%2C%20Seattle%20%E2%80%93%20in%201999.%20I%20was%20there%20to%20cover%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20Seattle%20Ministerial%20Meeting.%20That%20meeting%20collapsed%20like%20a%20pack%20of%20cards%20in%20the%20face%20of%20fierce%20and%20violent%20anti-globalisation%20protests.%20A%20day%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20professor%E2%80%99s%20home%20discussing%20Gaddar.%20I%20vividly%20remember%20what%20the%20professor%20said%20%E2%80%93%20he%20felt%20sad%20when%20he%20thought%20of%20Gaddar%20because%20he%20was%20a%20fine%20student%20and%20could%20have%20been%20teaching%20in%20any%20of%20the%20best%20universities%20today.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20Gaddar%2C%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20awakening%20the%20rural%20poor%20through%20his%20powerful%20folk%20songs%20%E2%80%93%20telling%20them%20that%20they%20can%20be%20independent%20one%20day%2C%20away%20from%20the%20feudal%20oppression%20that%20is%20aided%20and%20abetted%20by%20the%20state%20and%20its%20police%20machinery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20songs%20are%20electrifying.%20They%20would%20force%20one%20to%20think%20about%20their%20role%20in%20the%20society%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20they%20can%20do%20anything%20for%20uplifting%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20rural%20poor%20and%20tribals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20say%20that%20these%20songs%2C%20composed%20and%20sung%20by%20Gaddar%2C%20had%20enormous%20capacity%20to%20force%20you%20to%20think%20about%20the%20rural%20oppression%20of%20peasants%20and%20the%20tribal%20communities%C2%A0%20is%20an%20understatement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaddar%20mesmerised%20everyone%20with%20his%20group%20of%20three%20to%20four%20singers.%20For%20my%20brother%2C%20Gaddar%E2%80%99s%20famous%20song%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnm5O2wkCxzY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERela%20Re%2C%20Rela%20Re%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20morning%20ritual.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20not%20a%20moment%20when%20my%2078-year-old%20brother%20would%20not%20sing%20this%20particular%20song%20of%20Gaddar.%20It%20is%20a%20folk%20song%20that%20explains%20the%20daily%20existence%2C%20struggles%20and%20world%20view%20of%20tribal%20communities%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20song%20is%20a%20gem%20in%20itself.%20A%20moving%20song%20about%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20%E2%80%98Oh%20Police%20Anna%E2%80%99%20describes%20how%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20your%20life%2C%20their%20daily%20plight%20and%20our%20struggles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPNmDvOr1t0I%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20song%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgAipX6WfJyo%5C%22%3ENindu%20Amasanadu%20Oh%20Laccha%20Gummadi%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20explains%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20girl%2C%20how%20valuable%20it%20is%20and%20how%20she%20carries%20her%20daily%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRvgjQYsfAII%5C%22%3EBhadram%20Kodo%20Ku%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20cautions%20the%20city-bred%20officials%20to%20behave%20properly%C2%A0%20in%20the%20villages.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20also%20composed%20a%20song%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20people%20in%20Telangana%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href