agaur%20districts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20brought%20in%20instant%20milk%20chillers%20because%20the%20locations%20are%20spread%20out.%20By%20the%20time%2C%20these%20communities%20transported%20milk%20from%20one%20hamlet%20to%20another%20and%20then%20to%20the%20dairy%2C%20the%20milk%20would%20go%20bad%20amid%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20milk%20is%20brought%20to%20the%20dairy%20and%20milk%20processing%20units%20in%20Bajju%20village%20via%20delivery%20vans.%20Thereafter%2C%20products%20are%20made%20using%20camel%20and%20cow%20milk%2C%20which%20are%20then%20sold%20to%20300%20households%20across%20Bikaner%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20using%20a%20subscription%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173064%2Fmilk-cow-camel-almond-coconut-yak-goat-soy-coconut-alternative-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamel%20milk%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20camel%20milk%20biscuits%2C%20camel%20milk%20feta%20cheese%2C%20camel%20milk%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20A2%20cow%20%3Cem%3Ebilona%20ghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cold%20pressed%20oils%2C%20gluten-free%20black%20wheat%20flour%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakriti%20further%20informs%20that%20their%20cheese%20is%20now%20also%20procured%20by%20chefs%20in%20cities%20like%20Goa%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20to%20run%20such%20a%20startup%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20common%20for%20Indians%20to%20consume%20camel%20milk%20products.%20In%20the%20first%20year%2C%20most%20of%20our%20time%20was%20spent%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20camel%20milk%20products%2C%20which%20are%20highly%20nutritious%20superfoods.%20These%20products%20help%20people%20with%20d