ent-run%20%E2%80%9Copen%20school%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20explained%20concepts%20to%20me%20in%20my%20language%20and%20helped%20me%20read%20textbooks.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20memorising%20exact%20vocabulary%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20necessary%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wrote%20down%20what%20I%20understood.%20This%20approach%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20grasp%20the%20subjects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gubbachi%20mainstreams%20migrant%20children%20through%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fb44aafaa-d724-4fd0-af5d-359b0b5607d1-1690981573-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGubbachi%20mainstreams%20migrant%20children%20through%20various%20age-appropriate%20programmes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20hold%20of%20the%20basics%2C%20Vijay%20appeared%20for%20the%20Class%2010%20examination%20and%20secured%2088.5%20percent%20in%202021.%20Subsequently%2C