%A0and%20%3Cem%3Epuliohare%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamarind%20rice)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dabbas%20had%20gone%20out.%20No%20comments%20had%20come%20in%20an%20hour%20later.%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20everyone%20hates%20it%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20feeling%20of%20dejection%20lasted%20only%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20as%20appreciation%20suddenly%20began%20pouring%20in.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20messaged%20me%20saying%20that%20they%20loved%20it.%20And%20that%20rousing%20feedback%20made%20me%20believe%20in%20the%20idea.%20I%20began%20thinking%20that%20this%20could%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmongst%20the%20people%20who%20tried%20the%20first%20trial%20batch%20was%20Renee%2C%20who%20absolutely%20loved%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20%