lant%20requires%20one%20ton%20waste%2C%20we%20asked%20nearby%20restaurants%20to%20give%20their%20wet%20waste%2C%20as%20residents%20could%20produce%20only%20680-690%20kg%20per%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0After%20running%20the%20plant%20successfully%20for%20three%20years%2C%20PHRA%20handed%20over%20the%20plant%20to%20BMC%20in%202021%2C%20as%20per%20mutual%20agreement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stellar%20transformation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPHRA%20has%20scaled%20up%20their%20security%20too%2C%20in%20association%20with%20Khar%20police%2C%20say%20members.%20%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20security%20guards%2C%20we%20also%20have%2019%20high-definition%20night%20vision%20security%20cameras%20on%20our%20roads%2C%20which%20can%20even%20read%20a%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20number.%20They%20are%20monitored%20by%20Khar%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Sonu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20housekeeping%20team%20keeps%20the%20roads%20clean%20through%20regular%20sweeping%2C%20maintains%20the%20flower%20beds%20and%20saplings%20planted.%20Tree%20cutting%20is%20totally%20banned%20here%2C%20as%20is%20digging%20up%20roads%20by%20utilities%20without%20PHRA%E2%80%99s%20permission.%20To%20ensure%20proper%20resurfacing%20of%20roads%2C%20PHRA%20collects%20a%20refundable%20deposit%20from%20all%20utilities%20before%20they%20dig%20up%20the%20roads.%20Likewise%2C%20they%20have%20set%20some%20conditions%20for%20builders%20undertaking%20redevelopment%20at%20Pali%20Hill.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Pali%20Hill%2C%20Rajeev%20Kaushik%20an%20airline%20pilot%20who%20has%20witnessed%20the%20transformation%2C%20is%20all%20praise%20for%20PHRA%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CPali%20Hill%20looks%20very%20clean%20and%20green%20today.%20The%20biogas%20plant%20is%20an%20innovative%20project%20that%20is%20lighting%20up%20our%20streets%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310550%2Fengineer-quits-job-to-launch-india-first-electric-microcar-eas-e-kalpit-patel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20saving%20on%20electricity%20with%20zero%20carbon%20emission%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BMC%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBMC-1-1690871747-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0After%20running%20the%20plant%20successfully%20for%20three%20years%2C%20PHRA%20handed%20over%20the%20plant%20to%20BMC%20in%202021%2C%20as%20per%20mutual%20agreement.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20PHRA%20has%20won%20accolades%20individually%20and%20jointly%20with%20BMC%2C%C2%A0%20for%20their%20biogas%20plant%2C%20effective%20garbage%20management%20and%20in%20general%20for%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20environment.%20The%20awards%20are%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Housing%20%26amp%3B%20Urban%20Affairs%2C%20Skoch%20Group%20and%20Bhamla%20Foundation%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Our%20work%20will%20never%20stop%E2%80%99